CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 2, 1955, pg. 27 reads: "Dazzling Displays Exhibit Top Products at Fair...4. The fabulous Frankfort Distillers booth, stocked with Four Roses, Hunter and Paul Jones, was well represented by Lon Thompson of New York and Philadelphia, Sam Franke, district manager; Tom McGoire, Jack Peters and Steve Kirtis...Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Hunter Blended Whiskey booth, in Syria Mosque for the 1955 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
